crambles your financial date as it travels from your computer to our website; making is useless to anyone but Visa and MasterCard for processing the electronic purchase transaction for registration or merchandise.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Refund Policy</span></b>\n\n<b></b>Any approved refunds authorized by the Fairfax Stars Executive Director will be processed manually within 30 days.  Electronic refunds or credits are not available.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Shipping Policy</span></b>\n\nWe will ship merchandise via UPS delivery.  The cost of shipping is determined by the total amount of the purchase.  This is viewable when you check out with the shopping cart.','Terms','','publish','open','open','','terms','','','2014-02-26 21:17:51','2014-02-26 21:17:51','',0,'http://stars.jps26.com/?page_id=362',0,'page','',0),(366,1,'2014-02-26 21:25:17','2014-02-26 21:25:17','','Shop','','publish','open','open','','shop','','','2014-02-26 21:25:17','2014-02-26 21:25:17','',0,'http://stars.jps26.com/?page_id=366',0,'page','',0),(368,1,'2014-02-26 21:33:05','2014-02-26 21:33:05','<h3>Get in touch</h3>\n<div class=\"shortcode-hr mt-0 mp-30\"></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"center\">Please do not hesitate to contact us if you have questions or we may provide information.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"center\">If you wish to be added to our e-mail list to receive information about tournaments, camps, clinics or other important information, you may sign up on the home page or please send us an e-mail and let us know.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Address:</strong> 2801 Glade Vale Way Vienna, Virginia 22181</li>\n	<li><strong>Phone:</strong> 703-281-5203</li>\n	<li><strong>Fax:</strong> 703-281-5233</li>\n	<li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:fairfaxstars@aol.com\">fairfaxstars@aol.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"shortcode-hr mt-30 mp-40\"></div>\n<div class=\"shortcode-social-ico